dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Nipomo quadrangle, San Luis Obispo County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Nipomo, CA 1965, AMS 1954 III SW -- Series V895."
"Contour interval 40 feet, dotted lines represent 20 feet contours."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
